    <img src="IMAGES/MAKRKET INVESTMENTS (2).png" alt="Image 5">
</div>
  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <p style="color:darkslategray; font-weight: bold; font-size:30px;">
      ELEVATE YOUR BANKING EXPERIENCE WITH <br> THE BEST BANK IN PAKISTAN <br> ANYTIME, ANYWHERE
    </p>
